messages.msgSnippet: I just saw crumpets (8 for $1.39) and lemon curd (10.5 oz for $2.39) at Trader Joes today. Had to think of you all. I LOVE Trader Joes. ;-) Karin in Phoenix My
messages.messageBody:
I just saw crumpets (8 for $1.39) and lemon curd (10.5 oz for $2.39) at Trader Joes today. Had to think of you all.
I LOVE Trader Joes. ;-)


Karin
in Phoenix





My son love's Lemon Curd... in fact he just had it for lunch today....
Marmite is another favorite in our house (except husband whose American and
thinks it's horrible)...I can't get them to eat beans on toast, although
putting Heinz baked beans in Chili has worked out very well (LOL)...

Dawn
